  "title": "[Travel Opp] Brand ambassador",
  "description": "<p><strong>WANT TO EMBRACE THE NEW YOU?</strong></p><p>We are here looking out for you, so let us know if this interests you.</p><p>Join us for a high-energy team where you’ll learn real skills, meet amazing people, and build a resume that actually stands out. 🚀</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong> ✍🏻:</p><p>- Assist with events, roadshows & brand campaigns</p><p>- Learn face-to-face marketing & customer engagement</p><p>- Support the team in sales activities</p><p>- Find and attract new potential customers</p><p>- Work with fun and vibrant people</p><p><strong>With what you'll be doing, you get the following:</strong></p><p>- Attractive income 💰: The better performer you are, the higher the potential earnings that you can make. Your write your own paycheck.</p><p>- Travelling opportunities 🧳: Subjected to performance, you could be selected to our regional offices for learning and development. You just have to pack your luggage and flash your passport!</p><p>- On-going coaching provided 👨🏻‍🎓👩🏻‍🎓: The skills are portable. The skills you gained over time can be adapted into any markets. Be it business or personal.</p><p>- 👯‍♀️ Work with your friends : Bring your crew along.</p><p><strong>However, to start this journey, we will need the following from you:</strong></p><p>- Energetic, outgoing, and willing to learn</p><p>- Can commit full-time</p><p>- Good communication</p><p>- Able to perform in team and individually</p><p>- Eager to embrace challenges and work collaboratively within a team<br /></p><p>Join us now🤩</p>",
